#X text 27 95 AUTHOR Martin Werner;
#X text 27 135 VERSION 0.1;
#X text 27 65 DESCRIPTION A pd take on Fender's Harmonic Tremolo circuit
found in the "Brownface" amps of the early 1960s.;
